data.description: Beautiful newly remodeled split level with lots to offer! Remodeled kitchen with all new cabinets, quartz counter tops and appliances were installed 2021, new dishwasher as of 2023. All new carpet as of 2023. New 6-foot privacy fence built within the last 2 years. 1 built in garage with three car wide parking in driveway. Memorial Park is located across the street which offers playground, picnic area, and Frisbee golf course! Twin Rivers water park is located at the end of the street heading west and very nearby public schools. Great property and location overall! Any and all offers will be reviewed 4/8/2024 at 2:00PM.
